-------------------------------------------------------------- -- DESCRIPTION -- Get maintenance operator for recommendation by user from DB -------------------------------------------------------------- -- Revision Date Who What -- [DONE] [14 MAR 2023] [Muhammad Salman Al Farisyi] Initial Development --------------------------------------------------------------
